description_data.value: ** RESERVED ** This candidate has been reserved by an organization or individual that will use it when announcing a new security problem. When the candidate has been publicized, the details for this candidate will be provided.

descriptions.value: In modem driver, there is a possible system crash due to improper input validation. This could lead to local information disclosure with System execution privileges needed

En el controlador del módem, existe una posible falla del sistema debido a una validación de entrada incorrecta. Esto podría conducir a la divulgación de información local con privilegios de ejecución del System necesarios.
